# Tenant-specific context

> **Maintenance**: Update when catalog paths or tenant ids change (`rules-sync.mdc`).

## Catalogs

| Tenant ID | Catalog |
|-----------|---------|
| `vukans-bike` | `.cursor/rules/tenants/vukans-bike/catalog.mdc` |
| `resort-example` | `.cursor/rules/tenants/resort-example/catalog.mdc` |

## How to pick the tenant

1. `TENANT_ID` env / CI matrix / deploy workflow
2. Path: `src/tenants/{tenant-id}/`
3. Mock data: `vukans-bike` → `mock-data.ts/vukans-bike/`; `resort-example` → `mock-data.ts/resort/`

## Before editing tenant code

Read that tenant's catalog. After changes, update the catalog and any other rules listed in `rules-sync.mdc` — same turn, not a follow-up.
